How to prepare: Wear comfortable clothing you can move freely in, most classes are held barefoot and some people use socks with grip on them. Bring water if you'd like.

When to arrive: 15 minutes before

About this class: Our 50-minute Pilates Reformer group class. Elevate your fitness experience with a dynamic, full-body workout. Designed to strengthen, tone, and improve flexibility, this class targets every muscle with precision and control. Get ready to push your limits, feel empowered, and leave the studio stronger than ever!

About this studio: Let's Elevate Together! At ImoveAmsterdam Boutique Reformer Pilates Studio we are on a mission to Elevate your fitness experience. Offering  mind&body boosting Reformer Pilates Classes. Lets make some magic happen together.
